_:N3cc19469e93e40a797086e79966ca346 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Baroness Taylor of Stevenage was appointed Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State at the Ministry of Housing, Communities and Local Government and as a Baroness in Waiting (Government Whip) on 9 July 2024.</p>\n" .
